treatment. The results obtained from DNA flow cytometry could be associated with 
N, G, p53, Ki67 and metastases to lymph nodes. On the basis of the results 
obtained, the techniques suggested for the morphological and biological 
evaluation of neoplastic cells in cancer of the larynx should include TNM 
classification + G + DNA + p53 + Ki67.

